g.text: Verifier check the evidences and provide feedback

1.2 based on the cid unpack the .car file to its original file
1.3 verifies the evidence and provide feedback
1.4 pack the feedback to .car file and upload to Lighthouse

3.3 check if you only provide the evidence once
